RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

2010-1013. Hartford Fire Ins. Co. v. Seifert.

Cuyahoga App. No. 93291, 2010-Ohio-2346. Reported at 125 Ohio St.3d 1505, 2010-Ohio-3284, 929 N.E.2d 1071. On motion for reconsideration. Motion granted, and appellant shall file a memorandum in support of jurisdiction within 30 days of the date of this entry.
